so the days are winding down until school starts.... its kinda nerve wrecking... i still havent found out my roommate and im kinda anxious to know what he's like...&nbsp; i hope we get along..&nbsp;  so im kinda prepin for the move out and starting to pack up the shit...&nbsp; its kinda a wierd feeling.. and my mother isnt makin it better.... im bringing all this useless crap that i dont think i need and im gunna have no room to live in my dorm... the roommate im sure is gunna love that......&nbsp;  but other than that nothing much is goin on...&nbsp; i bought most of my class books today... talk about pricey... that one definitly hurt the wallet...&nbsp; &nbsp; 2 books and $267 later....&nbsp;  seems kinda rediculous for books if u ask me but what do i know.... im just a stupid college student....&nbsp;  

put another boring night up on the board for me..... i definitly spent 4 straight hours watching tv.... everyone who i called was busy... of course i find out later that melanie did the same thing tonite.... oh well&nbsp; &nbsp; next time ill remember to call her....

the more and more i read about and look at recording studios and things of that nature the more and more i wanna do that... on the other hand i still got my interest in politics and teaching... i wish i knew what i wanted to do...&nbsp; hopefully things will start to fall into place as i continue going to school.. i just hope i figure it all out soon so i can get out of school fast and move on with my life...

im kinda tired and im waitin for olivia to get into the poker room so i decided to write a little something.... i didnt do much at all today... i laid around til work, with the exception of starting my laundry, and the did nothing at work... it was kinda nice workin in the resturant for once... it can get kinda boring by urself though... ah well it beats doin tickets and that kinda stuff....&nbsp; 

nothing else is going on really&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; just bored&nbsp; &nbsp;  


